                        </desc>
                        <ptr target="http://syriaca.org/keyword/council-of-chalcedon-451 http://syriaca.org/keyword/persecution http://syriaca.org/keyword/monks http://syriaca.org/keyword/monastic-heads http://syriaca.org/keyword/theology"/>
